properties.Name: ExperianTradePayment
properties.Description: Experian trade payment information by business category.

Columns.Name: ExperianFileNumber
Columns.Description: The unique and persistent number that identifies and tracks the Experian company.

Columns.Name: ProfileTimestamp
Columns.Description: The timestamp of the Experian profile.

Columns.Name: ExperianBusinessCategoryTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Experian business category type.

Columns.Name: LastSaleDate
Columns.Description: The date of the last sale.

Columns.Name: BalanceAmount
Columns.Description: The outstanding balance amount of invoices.

Columns.Name: 130OutstandingAmount
Columns.Description:
The amount of invoices the company is paying 1-30 Days Beyond Terms (DBT).

Days Beyond Terms (DBT) is the average number of days a firm pays its bills past the invoice due date.

Columns.Name: 3160OutstandingAmount
Columns.Description:
The amount of invoices the company is paying 31-60 Days Beyond Terms (DBT).

Days Beyond Terms (DBT) is the average number of days a firm pays its bills past the invoice due date.

Columns.Name: 6190OutstandingAmount
Columns.Description:
The amount of invoices the company is paying 61-90 Days Beyond Terms (DBT).

Days Beyond Terms (DBT) is the average number of days a firm pays its bills past the invoice due date.

Columns.Name: 91PlusOutstandingAmount
Columns.Description:
The amount of invoices the company is paying 91+ Days Beyond Terms (DBT).

Days Beyond Terms (DBT) is the average number of days a firm pays its bills past the invoice due date.

Columns.Name: ExperianPaymentTermId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Experian payment term.

Columns.Name: Comment
Columns.Description:
A statement of comment regarding the trade payment experience.

Ex:
- PROMPT
- SATSFTRY
- CUST 6 YR

Columns.Name: ExperianTradePaymentTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Experian trade payment type.
